WEBVTT

00:02:59.871 --> 00:03:04.038
gapirishdan va bajarishdan
saqlaydigan katta qudratga ega. Va men

00:03:04.829 --> 00:03:06.496
o’zimga dedim, ”bilasan-mi nima?

00:03:06.496 --> 00:03:09.121
Qo’rquv meni hayotimni boshqarishiga
yo’l qo’ymayman”.

00:03:09.163 --> 00:03:12.579
Men qilmoqchi bo’lgan ishlarga qo’rquvga
yo’l qo’ymayman”.

00:03:12.579 --> 00:03:15.579
So’ngra barcha ajoyib narsalar 
boshlana yozdi

00:03:15.579 --> 00:03:17.163
va dominolar tushishni boshladi.

00:03:17.829 --> 00:03:20.538
Men shuni tushunib yetganimdan so’ng,
“Xo’sh, 2015 yil,

00:03:20.538 --> 00:03:21.829
30 yoshga to’ldim,

00:03:21.829 --> 00:03:24.038
bu yil meni qo’rqitadigan
har qanday narsani,

00:03:24.038 --> 00:03:27.079
faol ravishda ta’qib qilaman.”

00:03:27.663 --> 00:03:29.871
Mening burjim Uloq.

00:03:29.871 --> 00:03:31.996
Men yerda turishni yoqtiraman.